<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912675>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–17. Galápagos Diptera. 14, Chrysochlorina fasciata (Thomson) (Stratiomyidae), lateral view; 15, Tabanus vittiger Thomson (Tabanidae), lateral view; 16, Chersodromia galapagensis Sinclair & Cumming (Hybotidae), holotype (CNC), lateral view; 17, Toxomerus crockeri (Curran) (Syrphidae), dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912671>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–7. Galápagos habitats. 2, Tortuga Bay, Santa Cruz (1989); 3, Black Beach, Floreana (1989); 4, Floreana, arid zone (March, 1989); 5, Santa Fé, Malaise trap, arid zone (April 1989); 6, rotting Jasminocereus cactus branch; inset: empty puparia of Chrysochlorina fasciata (Thomson); 7, marine iguana dung on beach, Sesuvium sp. in background, Santa Cruz." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912671/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

